Type "# You can install fonts in non-interactive way by passing their names as arguments or comma-separated"
Enter

Type "./install.sh ibmplexmono,Ubuntu tERMiNuS --quiet"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Wait
Screenshot media/screenshots/04-batch.png
Type "# Fonts were installed in directory:"
Sleep 2s
Enter
Type "ls -lah ${HOME}/.local/share/fonts"
Enter
Wait
Sleep 5s
